{"tid":2300434,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"習近平致電拜登祝賀對方當選美國總統","createTime":"2020-11-25T13:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T14:01:29.000Z","uid":155431,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"282bfd099baf3fecc613a8ca0ff908889e95c98e","tid":2300434,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平致電拜登，祝賀他當選美國總統。<br />\n<br />\n新華社引述習近平在賀電中指出，推動中美關係健康穩定發展，不單止符合兩國人民根本利益，而且是國際社會的共同期待，希望雙方秉持不衝突不對抗、相互尊重、合作共贏的精神，聚焦合作，管控分歧，推動中美關係健康穩定向前發展，與各國和國際社會攜手推進世界和平與發展的崇高事業。<br />\n　　<br />\n另外，國家副主席王岐山致電賀錦麗，祝賀對方當選美國副總統。<br />\n<br />\n2020-11-25 HKT 21:35 RTHK"},{"pid":"cb00e2a45de9559fe4b26f9afb38368d1a435ec3","tid":2300434,"uid":155431,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"習近平說，希望雙方秉持不衝突不對抗、相互尊重、合作共贏的精神，聚焦合作，管控分歧。"},{"pid":"0c3634f6595df88f9b4b816afff017d28cba3c19","tid":2300434,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T13:41:27.000Z","msg":"Link: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561995-20201125.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561995-20201125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=ee25bc3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561995-20201125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=440179a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561995-20201125.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"30683eafaf490a89d5e49c6dd382ee9d7da71f00","tid":2300434,"uid":24570,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"終於發出賀電<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/angry_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2178c823d913dfaf5adeaed8a96e601b33ec4d","tid":2300434,"uid":7860,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"其實佢地係咪用